snippet.title: Doctor Dekker 2 - Announcement FMV Game Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist now ⬇️ 🙏
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2939680/The_Infectious_Madness_of_Doctor_Dekker_2/

An FMV game where YOU are a psychiatrist trying to solve a double murder whilst treating the unusual patients of the recently deceased Doctor Dekker. Ask questions and link answers to determine their fates, and your own!

The Infectious Madness of Doctor Dekker 2 is the 5th FMV videogame from D'Avekki Studios.

Linktree : https://linktr.ee/davekki

Doctor Dekker Website : https://doctordekker.com/

Teaser music : Tim Cowles.

"Marianna" voiceover by Aislinn De'Ath ❤️
